title: Learn a word
description: A simple website that allows users to learn random words by retyping the definition. In addition, a side game named 'Cuppy' (inspired by Hangman) is used to grab a random word that the user has learned to review.

title: Charles River Watershed Map
description: Designed a user-friendly interactive restoration map for the Charles River.

title: RantHub
description: A website for ranting and listening anonymously.

title: Summary of the Population Under 18 Years Old
description: The bubble chart displays the population under 18 years old based on different housing types with the size of the bubbles characterizing the size of the population. The pink bubbles represent the population living in multifamily housing zones, and the purple bubbles represent the population living in single-family housing zones.

title: UnitedPlanet Website for volunteers
description: Built a full stack system for coordinators to organize data for volunteers

title: Math Fish Pygame
description: Constructed an educational math game targeting elementary students using Pygame with three other students.
